<emphasis id="82E96703DDE16F09DD262DB1C5A719E7" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="97">Figure 3.</emphasis>
Ovipositor. Female. 
<emphasis id="06F3A3219A88A2C544D482924DABA67F" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="97">A-E</emphasis>
